Dancehall star, Sean Paul has returned with another potential hit track “When It Comes To You”. On this one, he joins forces with the top Nigerian female songstress, Tiwa Savage and prolific DJ Spinall to dish out the remix groove-worthy song. After the success of his recently released track “Buss A Bubble”, the singer decides to thrill his music fans with this new monster-piece definitely worth listening to. Of course Tiwa Savage and DJ Spinall’s input showed the collaboration wasn’t a waste of time. Listen and Enjoy Below! 